month_score <- okja %>%
  select(, ) %>%
  group_by() %>%
  summarise(month_score_mean = mean()) %>%
  arrange(month_score_mean)

#   
ggplot(month_score, aes(x= reorder(, -month_score_mean), y=month_score_mean, fill = )) +
  geom_bar(stat = 'identity', color = 'black') +
  ggtitle('  ') +
  xlab('') +
  ylab('') +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size=20, color = 'red',
                                  hjust = 0.5, vjust=0)) +
  theme(axis.title.x = element_text(size = 15, color = 'red',
                                    hjust = 0.5, vjust = 0)) +
  theme(axis.title.y = element_text(size= 15, color = 'red',
                                    hjust = 0.5, vjust = 0)) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle=90, size = 10, color='black')) +
  theme(axis.text.y = element_text(angle=0, size = 10, color='black')) +
  theme(legend.title = element_blank()) +
  theme(legend.position = 'none') + 
  geom_text(aes(y=month_score_mean - 0.2, label= paste(round(month_score_mean,1), '')),
            color='black', size=4)
